result.name: Tasty Star

reviews.text: A very nice restaurant.
Cheap and food is good for the price

This excellent little restaurant serves authentic and good quality Chinese dim sum and dishes. Best of all it is very inexpensive. Chose a set-menu (set A/B/C etc. ) for about $45 HKD and get a dimsum mix, meal and a drink !! Or just select a number of traditional Dim Sum for about $20 HKD. 
Service is good and a modern interior. 
When you are done you can get right back with shopping at Fa Yuen Street :-).
Not a tasty star at all...
Meh
